Token:
- Cost (float): fixed ($0.25 / token) (global var?)

Game:
- Name
- Cost (int): fixed (4 tokens per game)

Ledger (list of transactions). Transaction:
- BoughtToken/SpentToken (?)
- Number of tokens (int)
- Description of action (String)

------------------------

Pages/Modules:
- Arcade: List of games with token values (shows # tokens)
- Buy Tokens: Can buy X tokens (shows token cost)
- Ledger: Shows transaction history